FT  30 NOV 94 / Budget 94 (Government Statements): VAT thresholds to be
increased
VAT registration and deregistration thresholds are to be increased.
From midnight, the annual turnover above which VAT registration is
compulsory increased to Pounds 46,000 from Pounds 45,000 and the
deregistration threshold to Pounds 44,000 from Pounds 43,000. From January 1
1995, the registration and deregistration thresholds for acquisitions from
other European Union countries will also rise, in both cases to Pounds
46,000 from Pounds 45,000.
